task.summary: - modified ArrayUtil.class.php, added UTF8encoding functionality - modified Connection.class.php, added default SQL filters passed in as array to query() method - added ConnectionBuilder.class.php, will create a new database Connection object with values loaded from DatabaseConfiguration file - modified XmlDocument.class.php, fixed type in PhpDoc - added AbstractDatabaseModel.class.php, base class for all database models - modified ControllerLoader.class.php, fixed a bug where strpos() was used instead of strrpos() to determine controller name

- modified loader.php, added correct include path file check - modified Configuration.class.php, get function now using multi dimensional key to retrieve value from Configuration - modified Connection.Configuration.class.php, added QueryExtension as WHERE clause, added showTables routine to list tables found in a database - added QueryExtender.class.php to allow setting various SQL filters - modified MssqlConnection.class.php, added brackets in mssql_select_db (dash in db name will otherwise cause errors), added showTables routine - modified OracleConnection.class.php, added showTables routine - modifed AbstractDatabaseModel.class.php, addes sort routine - added JqGridModel.class.php, minimalistic structure for backends returning values to JQGrid - modified Registry.class.php, added overwrite value when returning a key - added AbstractBackend.class.php. base for all backends - added ResponseState.class.php, enumeration for response states - added ResponseFactory.class.php, returns an instance of a given response class (currently Base (HTML) and JSON) - added BaseResponse.class.php, returns unparsed data - added JsonResponse.class.php, returns JSON-encoded data - modified framework.php, removed unnecessary includes
- added Array functions i.e. UTF8-encoding and Array sort functions - modified Connection class to add QueryExtender clause at the right position
